column5: Very nice G.  Sweatshirt weather, bah humbug  Joey

Eee doggies, Glen, you always seem to have some beauts.  I think you freeze and unthaw them to show over and over.

Good deal Glen.  Gald to see you're able to get out there.   I'm hoping to get out myself in the next month or so.   Got me a new puppy that I've got to get "boat-broken".     Hope this goes better than the "House-Breaking"
Good deal Glen!  Chris that is one BA crappie!

Not bad for a days work Glen!  I was thinkin yesterday of parking the boat in the garage, unwrap her and start working on it for spring....then I heard we're getting another 20cm of snow Friday night into Saturday.  When will the madness stop?????
Nice pics glen.. now you have the bait...
Looking good Glen nice looking slabs  For a change your winshield is wet not your pants
Out with the sabiki again were ya? While you were sitting in the boat, I was out shubblin the driveway. I hope you're satified. I don't even know if we have white crappie here. Thanks for showing.
